div.p:
ORdered That Doctor Palmer, Mr. Nevil, Mr. Oldſworth, Mr. Moile, Mr. Millington, Mr. Dormer, Mr. Peter Temple, and Mr. Rous, or any two of them be a Sub-Committee;
to conſider of the Book this day preſented to this Committee, Entituled, The Petition and Argument of Mr. Hotham, &c. And to Report their opinions concerning
the ſame to this Committee on this day ſeven night.
